{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require sound emitters on electric cars to be permanently switched on",
        "additional_details": "There have been several instances of visually-impaired people coming close to serious injury due to not hearing an electric vehicle approaching.\r\n\r\nSound emitters should be on at all times.",
        "background": "Make it a legal requirement that all electric vehicles are fitted with sound emitters and that these devices are always switched on.",
